used sound to chant

00:47:59.590 --> 00:48:05.690 align:middle line:84%
to plants in order to encourage
growth of different kinds.

00:48:05.690 --> 00:48:08.350 align:middle line:84%
People in India, and
this is certainly

00:48:08.350 --> 00:48:10.050 align:middle line:84%
something that's
happened all over.

00:48:10.050 --> 00:48:12.500 align:middle line:84%
And playing music to
plants, of course,

00:48:12.500 --> 00:48:14.710 align:middle line:84%
they find that they like
Mozart, and they like this,

00:48:14.710 --> 00:48:15.780 align:middle line:90%
