>>PURCE: One of the earlier--

00:48:20.270 --> 00:48:20.740 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:48:20.740 --> 00:48:21.730 align:middle line:90%
>>PURCE: --people who did this.

00:48:21.730 --> 00:48:22.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:48:22.690 --> 00:48:25.610 align:middle line:84%
And then let's go back to your
sons, and singing, and tone,

00:48:25.610 --> 00:48:27.320 align:middle line:90%
and helping them pass exams.

00:48:27.320 --> 00:48:29.860 align:middle line:84%
I think people find this
very practical and useful

00:48:29.860 --> 00:48:32.317 align:middle line:84%
if we can find a pure
note within ourselves.

00:48:32.317 --> 00:48:34.150 align:middle line:84%
>>PURCE: Well, there
are lots of reasons why

00:48:34.150 --> 00:48:35.690 align:middle line:90%
