00:55:30.040 --> 00:55:33.610 align:middle line:84%
So just making a continuous
sound on one note,

00:55:33.610 --> 00:55:38.230 align:middle line:84%
and all the time that
you're making that sound,

00:55:38.230 --> 00:55:41.110 align:middle line:84%
allowing it to be
integrated with the vessel

00:55:41.110 --> 00:55:42.470 align:middle line:90%
of your hearing.

00:55:42.470 --> 00:55:44.860 align:middle line:84%
So there is no moment
when you're not

00:55:44.860 --> 00:55:50.140 align:middle line:84%
hearing through this intracative
listening, not judging good,

00:55:50.140 --> 00:55:55.030 align:middle line:84%
